flowchart LR
  C[Client] -->|POST /orders| O[Order Service]
  O -->|gRPC ProcessPayment| P[Payment Service]
  P -->|Publish JSON event| EX[(RabbitMQ Exchange\npayment.events)]
  EX --> Q[(Queue\npayment.completed)]
  Q --> N[Notification Service]
  N -->|Manual ACK after log| Q
  N --> DB[(notification_db\nprocessed_events)]
  N -->|Duplicate event_id| Skip[ACK without duplicate log]
  N -->|DLQ demo after retries| DLX[(payment.dlx)]
  DLX --> DLQ[(payment.completed.dlq)]
